This is delicious, fast, easy and healthy! Including prep time for chopping, etc., it took about 45 minutes to make this hearty, spicy soup. I added 3 cubed potatoes (with skin) to the onions and carrots, doubled the amount of curry, and threw in a package of frozen peas with the broth. If I serve this to company I will garnish with a dollop of sour cream or creme fraiche, for presentation and to cut the spice for those who like it milder. I will make this again and again!

